   Scrap Metal / Scrap Car
<% end %>

<% content_for :body do %>
The owner of the vehicle must complete the back of the Vehicle Registration Document by ticking the 'scrapped' box, signing and entering the date the vehicle was scrapped in box number one.  This document should be sent to DVS within seven days.
It can then be taken to the waste metals recycling facility in Bellozanne.
